#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:6
msgid "Spin"
msgstr "旋绕"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:8
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "模式"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:11
msgid "Edit Mode"
msgstr "编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "面板"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:12
msgid ":menuselection:`Tool Shelf --> Tools --> Mesh Tools --> Add: Spin`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`工具栏 --> 工具 --> 网格工具 --> 添加: 旋绕`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst
msgid "Hotkey"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:13
msgid ":kbd:`Alt-R`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt-R`"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:15
msgid ""
"The *Spin* tool extrudes (or duplicates it if the selection is manifold) the "
"selected elements, rotating around a specific point and axis."
msgstr "*旋绕* 工具绕特定点和轴向旋转，挤出(当选中项为流形时复制)选中元素。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:18
msgid ""
"Use the tool to create the sort of objects that you would produce on a lathe "
"(this tool is often called a \"lathe\"-tool or a \"sweep\"-tool in the "
"literature, for this reason). In fact, it does a sort of circular extrusion of "
"your selected elements, centered on the 3D cursor, and around the axis "
"perpendicular to the working view..."
msgstr ""
"使用 *旋绕* 工具来生成类似车床做出的结果(因为这个原因，该工具常被称做\"旋转\"或"
"\"扫掠\" )。事实上，它确实是以3D游标为中心，并且围绕着垂直于工作视图的轴向，生"
"成选中元素的某种环状挤出。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:23
msgid "The point of view will determine around which axis the extrusion spins..."
msgstr "观察点决定挤出围绕的轴向。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:24
msgid "The position of the 3D cursor will be the center of the rotation."
msgstr "3D游标的位置将是旋绕的中心。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:28
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:30
msgid "Steps"
msgstr "步数"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:31
msgid "Specifies how many copies will be extruded along the \"sweep\"."
msgstr "指定\"扫掠\"后挤出的复制体数量。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:33
#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:99
msgid "Dupli"
msgstr "复制"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:33
msgid ""
"When enabled, will keep the original selected elements as separated islands in "
"the mesh (i.e. unlinked to the result of the spin extrusion)."
msgstr "选中时，原始结构与旋绕结果是分开的独立结构(即与旋绕挤出的结果断开)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:35
#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:81
msgid "Angle"
msgstr "角度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:36
msgid ""
"Specifies the angle \"swept\" by this tool, in degrees (e.g. set it to 180 for "
"half a turn)."
msgstr "指定旋绕\"扫过\"的角度，单位度(比如，180表示半圈)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:37
msgid "Center"
msgstr "中心"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:38
msgid "Specifies the center of the spin. By default it uses the cursor position."
msgstr "指定旋绕的中心，默认使用3D游标位置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:41
msgid "Axis"
msgstr "轴向"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:40
msgid ""
"Specify the spin axis as a vector. By default it uses the view axis (viewport)."
msgstr "指定旋绕表示轴向的向量，默认使用当前视角轴向(视图)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:44
msgid "Example"
msgstr "范例"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:51
msgid "Glass profile."
msgstr "杯子轮廓。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:53
msgid ""
"First, create a mesh representing the profile of your object. If you are "
"modeling a hollow object, it is a good idea to thicken the outline. Fig. :ref:"
"`fig-mesh-spin-glass` shows the profile for a wine glass we will model as a "
"demonstration."
msgstr ""
"首先，为物体创建表示轮廓的网格。如果需要建模的是中空物体，对轮廓线直接加厚也不"
"错。图 :ref:`fig-mesh-spin-glass` 展示了我们即将演示建模过程的酒杯的轮廓。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:57
msgid ""
"Go to *Edit Mode* and select all the vertices of the Profile with :kbd:`A`."
msgstr "进入 *编辑模式*，按下 :kbd:`A` 全选轮廓的所有顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:59
msgid ""
"We will be rotating the object around the cursor in the top view, so switch to "
"the top view with :kbd:`Numpad7`."
msgstr ""
"我们将在顶视图围绕3D游标旋绕这个对象，因此按下 :kbd:`Numpad7` 切换到顶视图。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:67
msgid "Glass profile, top view in Edit Mode, just before spinning."
msgstr "旋绕之前，编辑模式下杯子轮廓的顶视图。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:69
msgid ""
"Place the cursor along the center of the profile by selecting one of the "
"vertices along the center, and snapping the 3D cursor to that location with :"
"menuselection:`Mesh --> Cursor --> Selection`. (Fig. :ref:`fig-mesh-spin-glass-"
"top`) shows the wine glass profile from top view, with the cursor correctly "
"positioned."
msgstr ""
"沿中心线选择一个顶点，再使用 :menuselection:`网格 --> 游标 --> 选中项` 将3D游标"
"吸附到选中点的位置，这样将游标置于轮廓的中心。(图 :ref:`fig-mesh-spin-glass-"
"top`)显示了顶视图下的酒杯轮廓，游标已放置到正确位置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:74
msgid ""
"Click the *Spin* button. If you have more than one 3D View open, the cursor "
"will change to an arrow with a question mark and you will have to click in the "
"area containing the top view before continuing. If you have only one 3D View "
"open, the spin will happen immediately. Fig. :ref:`fig-mesh-spin-profile` "
"shows the result of a successful spin."
msgstr ""
"点击 *旋绕* 按钮。若打开的3D视图不只1个，光标将变成带问号的箭头，需要在顶视图所"
"在区域单击方可继续。若你只打开了1个3D视图，旋绕操作将立即进行。图 :ref:`fig-"
"mesh-spin-profile` 显示了成功旋绕的结果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:85
msgid "Spun profile."
msgstr "旋绕后的轮廓。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:90
msgid "Spun profile using an angle of 360."
msgstr "360度旋绕后的轮廓。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:95
msgid "Spun profile using an angle of 120."
msgstr "120度旋绕后的轮廓。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:106
msgid "Result of spin operation."
msgstr "旋绕操作的结果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:111
msgid "Result of Dupli enabled."
msgstr "勾选复制的结果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:115
msgid "Merge Duplicates"
msgstr "合并重叠点"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:122
msgid "Duplicate vertices."
msgstr "重叠点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:124
msgid ""
"The spin operation leaves duplicate vertices along the profile. You can select "
"all vertices at the seam with Border select :kbd:`B` (shown in Fig. :ref:`fig-"
"mesh-screw-duplicate`) and perform a *Remove Doubles* operation."
msgstr ""
"旋绕操作会留下重叠点。你可以用框选 :kbd:`B` 来选择接缝处所有的顶点(如图 :ref:"
"`fig-mesh-screw-duplicate`)，然后执行 *移除重叠点* 操作。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:128
msgid ""
"Notice the selected vertex count before and after the *Remove Doubles* "
"operation ``Vertex count after removing doubles``. If all goes well, the final "
"vertex count (38 in this example) should match the number of the original "
"profile noted in :menuselection:`Mesh data --> Vertex and face numbers`. If "
"not, some vertices were missed and you will need to weld them manually. Or, "
"worse, too many vertices will have been merged."
msgstr ""
"注意 *移除重叠点* 前后选中顶点的数目。若一切顺利，最终顶点数(本例中为38)应该与"
"原始轮廓的顶点数量一致，顶点数量的查看方式在 :menuselection:`网格数据 --> 顶点"
"与面数量` 已经介绍过了。如不一致，应该是遗漏了某些顶点，你需要手动焊接。如果太"
"多的顶点需要合并，情况会更糟。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:135
msgid "Merging Two Vertices into One"
msgstr "合并两个顶点为一个"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:137
msgid ""
"To merge (weld) two vertices together, select both of them by :kbd:`Shift-RMB` "
"clicking on them. Press :kbd:`S` to start scaling and hold down :kbd:`Ctrl` "
"while scaling to scale the points down to 0 units in the X, Y and Z axis. :kbd:"
"`LMB` to complete the scaling operation and click the *Remove Doubles* button "
"in the Tool Shelf in *Edit Mode* (also available with :menuselection:`Specials "
"--> Remove Doubles`)."
msgstr ""
"要把两个顶点合并(焊接)到一起， :kbd:`Shift-RMB` 点击同时选中两个顶点。按下 :"
"kbd:`S` 开始缩放，并在缩放时按住 :kbd:`Ctrl` ，沿X，Y，Z方向都缩放到0。 :kbd:"
"`LMB` 单击完成缩放操作，并点击工具栏中的 *移除重叠点* 按钮(也可以使用 :"
"menuselection:`专用项 --> 移除重叠点`)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:143
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can use :menuselection:`Specials --> Merge` from the same "
"*Specials* menu (or :kbd:`Alt-M`). Then, in the new pop-up menu, choose "
"whether the merged vertex will be at the center of the selected vertices or at "
"the 3D cursor. The first choice is better in our case!"
msgstr ""
"另外，还可以在专用项菜单选择 :menuselection:`专用项 --> 合并` (或快捷键 :kbd:"
"`Alt-M`)。然后，在弹出菜单中，选择合并的顶点位于选中点的中心还是在3D游标处。在"
"本例中第一个选择更好！"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:150
msgid "Recalculate Normals"
msgstr "重新计算法线"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/duplicating/spin.rst:152
msgid ""
"All that remains now is to recalculate the normals to the outside by selecting "
"all vertices, pressing :kbd:`Ctrl-N` and validating *Recalculate Normals "
"Outside* in the pop-up menu."
msgstr ""
"现在就只剩下全选所有顶点，按下 :kbd:`Ctrl-N` ，在弹出菜单中选择 *向外重算法线方"
"向*。"

